description: ANN Late(ish) is a news program hosted by the General Conference Youth Departments Kenia Reyes and Mweyna Mpundu. Each night, at 9:30 they will break down the days GC Session news, share funny stories from their first experience at GC Session and interview Youth Leaders from around the world.
